<topic id='element_death_cause_recorded_text.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Data Element: DEATH CAUSE RECORDED TEXT - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_death_cause_recorded_text">DEATH CAUSE RECORDED TEXT</xref>
 is the same as attribute 
              <xref outputclass="attribute"
               keyref="attribute_person_observation_text_string">PERSON OBSERVATION TEXT STRING</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_death_cause_recorded_text">DEATH CAUSE RECORDED TEXT</xref>
 is the cause of death as recorded on the death certificate.        </p>
      <p>
The information for the following 
              <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_death_cause_recorded_text">DEATH CAUSE RECORDED TEXT</xref>
 Data Elements is taken from the Medical Certificate of Cause of Death:        </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
I(a): 
                                <xref outputclass="element"
                        keyref="element_death_cause_recorded_text__immediate_condition_">DEATH CAUSE RECORDED TEXT (IMMEDIATE CONDITION)</xref>
               </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
I(b): 
                                <xref outputclass="element"
                        keyref="element_death_cause_recorded_text__due_to_condition_">DEATH CAUSE RECORDED TEXT (DUE TO CONDITION)</xref>
               </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
I(c): 
                                <xref outputclass="element"
                        keyref="element_death_cause_recorded_text__other_condition_">DEATH CAUSE RECORDED TEXT (OTHER CONDITION)</xref>
               </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
II: 
                                <xref outputclass="element"
                        keyref="element_death_cause_recorded_text__contributing_condition_">DEATH CAUSE RECORDED TEXT (CONTRIBUTING CONDITION)</xref>
               </p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>For further information regarding the Medical Certificate of Cause of Death, see:</p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <p>
The 
                          <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_office_for_national_statistics">Office for National Statistics</xref>
 document 
                          <xref href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/guidance-notes-for-completing-a-medical-certificate-of-cause-of-death"
                     scope="external"
                     format="html">Guidance for doctors completing Medical Certificates of Cause of Death in England and Wales</xref>
            </p>
            <ul>
               <li>
                  <p>
This document advises Doctors how to complete the Death Certificate and also contains information on how the 
                                      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                           keyref="business_definition_office_for_national_statistics">Office for National Statistics</xref>
 code the text.                        </p>
               </li>
            </ul>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
The 
                          <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_office_for_national_statistics">Office for National Statistics</xref>
 website at: 
                          <xref href="https://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20160105231503/http://www.ons.gov.uk/ons/guide-method/user-guidance/health-and-life-events/index.html"
                     scope="external"
                     format="html">Health and life events guidance and metadata</xref>
            </p>
            <ul>
               <li>
                  <p>See the Mortality metadata document. Annex A shows the Medical Certificate of Cause of Death.</p>
               </li>
            </ul>
         </li>
      </ul>
  </div>
</body>
